36:35.735 --> 36:38.362
       [Tina] I get it. Okay.       

36:38.404 --> 36:39.614
             Um, yeah--             

36:39.655 --> 36:41.449
   I'll get you the contact info.   

36:41.490 --> 36:42.825
 [Mel] Um, I'll set something up. 

36:42.867 --> 36:44.702
        [Tina] Okay. Thanks.        

36:48.748 --> 36:50.082
            [door closes]           

36:52.418 --> 36:53.461
           [Marian sighs]           

37:03.137 --> 37:04.764
