         at night the most.         

37:54.146 --> 37:55.147
          You're right.             

37:55.189 --> 37:56.232
         Something like that        

37:56.274 --> 37:57.608
       happened to one of you!      

37:58.526 --> 38:00.152
                Yeah.               

38:00.194 --> 38:02.905
